<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原來你也來幫<delay20 />
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />慶祝生日啦？<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你這麼重視死黨，精神值得欽佩啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了幫<gender3 m="他" f="她" />過一個最棒的生日，<delay20 />
我覺得我也要貢獻一己之力才行！<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來吧，<delay20 />你也<delay8 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗨起來！<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的生日，
<gender3 m="他" f="她" />可是主角！<delay20 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我們這群死黨<delay8 />
可一定要把氣氛炒熱到最高點啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要看到<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />高興的樣子，<delay20 />
感覺就連我們也會跟著揚起嘴角哩！</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你快看，<delay20 /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />露出笑容啦！<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><gender3 m="他" f="她" />這麼雀躍的樣子<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是很少見的喔！？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了舉辦一場最棒的慶生會，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們今天也要<delay8 />
嗨到最高點啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯？<delay20 />我沒見過你吧？<delay40 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的名字是<tag a="110" b="10" />喔！<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能在這裡相遇，也算有某種緣分呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的生日吧？<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這可是我死黨誕生的特別日子，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我想說，要來好好炒熱一下氣氛呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，我還因此得以認識你，<delay20 />
對我來說，今天也變成特別的日子啦！<delay40 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今後也請多指教囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />幫死黨慶祝生日<delay20 />
還真是開心啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />無論是明年<delay8 />還是後年，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我都想用全力幫死黨慶祝啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這場生日派對，<delay20 />你玩得還開心嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />也很開心，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是不枉費我努力準備啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果我的生日派對<delay20 />
也能這麼熱鬧的話就好啦！</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為什麼<delay20 />生日蛋糕這東西……<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是看到它裝飾在那裡，<delay20 />
就會讓人忍不住亢奮起來啊？<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我以前有個夢想，<delay20 />
就是要一個人吃掉整個蛋糕，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是最近，我完全不這麼想了呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比起一個人獨享，<delay20 />還是跟死黨一起吃<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺會更好吃吧？<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難道我也變得成熟了嗎？</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你不覺得生日派對的會場<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />裝飾得實在很讚嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這是昨天<delay20 />我們一起努力布置的喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要把房間布置得比平常更華麗，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就會有生日的特別感覺，不賴吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能像這樣，<delay20 />幫死黨慶祝<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />新的一年的開始，<delay20 />實在讓人高興啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><delay20 />
也很享受這場派對，<delay20 />真是太好啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已經把生日禮物<delay20 />
交給<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我昨天<delay20 />跟<gender3 m="他" f="她" />小聊一下的時候，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺<gender3 m="他" f="她" />好像<delay20 />
很期待你送的禮物喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />別擔心，<delay20 />這種東西貴在心意。<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要是你用心挑選的東西，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />無論是什麼，對方一定都會覺得高興的。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />打從以前開始，<delay20 />
我就不太擅長<delay8 />挑禮物呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />甚至有時候，禮物到頭來都沒送出去。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<delay20 /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我後來發現，送禮物的意義<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不在於禮物，而是在於「送」這件事。<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以<delay20 />你也提起勇氣，<delay20 />送出禮物看看吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想如果是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay20 />
光是知道你送禮物給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />無論收到什麼，都會很高興吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要送什麼生日禮物<delay20 />
給<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />啊？<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我挑了很普通的日常用品，<delay20 />
但稍微冒險一下<delay8 />或許也不錯吧。<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下次我就<delay20 />稍微變點花樣好了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喔喔，<delay20 />這不是<tag a="110" b="3" />嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也搬來<delay8 />這座島上哩。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以後就請多關照囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後我今天是來參加<delay8 />
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的生日派對啦。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也跟我們一起<delay8 />炒熱派對氣氛吧！</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦，<delay20 />這不是<tag a="110" b="3" />嗎！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真沒想到會在這裡遇到你啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在<delay8 />就住在這座島上哩！<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的生日，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以正在幫<gender3 m="他" f="她" />慶生喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果不嫌棄，<delay20 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也加入我們吧！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦，<delay20 />你好像是生面孔耶！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的名字<delay8 />叫做<tag a="110" b="10" />。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不嫌棄的話，就記下來吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天呢，我被找來參加<delay8 />
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的慶生會！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要不要也一起來慶祝啊？</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天好忙啊～！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的生日，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還有情人節，活動超級多的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個送你吧！</message>
	<message label="020_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是啊～</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我覺得死黨的生日比較重要，<delay40 />
但是聽說其他人都忙著慶祝情人節啊。<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天真的<delay8 />到處都很熱鬧呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不嫌棄的話，請收下這個</message>
	<message label="021_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也許是吧</message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是死黨的生日就夠特別了，<delay20 />
今天竟然還是情人節。<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是<delay8 />難得的一天啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="022_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />收下這個吧！</message>
	<message label="022_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說得沒錯</message>
</msbt>